snippet.title: Rocket League® - Supersonic Fury DLC Pack Trailer
snippet.description:
Expand your Rocket League customization options with Supersonic Fury DLC Pack! This add-on includes...

* 2 new Battle-Cars, Dominus and Takumi
* 6 unique Decals for each new Battle-Car (12 total)
* 5 new Paint Types
* 2 new Rocket Boosts
* 2 new Wheels
